sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor NV as Nhan vien
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Staff as Staff Service
    participant StaffDB as Staff DB - MongoDB

    NV->>GW: PUT /api/staff/employees/:employeeId/availability
    Note over NV,GW: availableDays - danh sach ngay ranh<br/>availableTimeRanges - khung gio ranh
    GW->>Staff: Forward request - yeu cau auth EMPLOYEE

    Staff->>StaffDB: employee.findByEmployeeId(employeeId)
    StaffDB-->>Staff: employee record

    alt Nhan vien khong ton tai
        Staff-->>GW: 404 Not Found
        GW-->>NV: Khong tim thay nhan vien
    else accountId khong khop voi nguoi dang dang nhap
        Staff-->>GW: 403 Forbidden
        GW-->>NV: Ban chi co the cap nhat lich ranh cua ban than
    else Nhan vien toan thoi gian - FULL_TIME
        Staff-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
        GW-->>NV: Nhan vien toan thoi gian khong can dat lich ranh
    else Hop le - chi PART_TIME
        Staff->>StaffDB: availability.createOrUpdate(employeeId, data)
        Note over Staff,StaffDB: Upsert - tao moi neu chua co<br/>cap nhat neu da co<br/>availableDays - MON, TUE, SAT...<br/>availableTimeRanges - start, end
        StaffDB-->>Staff: availability record

        Staff-->>GW: 200 OK
        Note over Staff,GW: employeeId, availableDays<br/>availableTimeRanges
        GW-->>NV: Cap nhat lich ranh thanh cong
    end
